headline.print_headline: Pakistan Spinners Strike After Younus, Shehzad Heroics
headline.main: Pakistan Spinners Strike After Younus, Shehzad Heroics

lead_paragraph: Pakistan's spinners scythed through Australia's top order in the second innings to get them close to victory in the first test after twin centuries from Younus Khan and youngster Ajmal Shehzad helped the hosts set an improbable target.
